title: The Townhall Weekend Journal for SEP-20-2013 FRI

The Townhall Weekend Journal for SEP-20-2013 FRI






Friday, September 20, 2013


What to Make of Syria?





Weekend Journal 







Bill Bennett and Michael Rubin on Syria. Michael Medved and Joe Lieberman on Syria.
